                        <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="def1-884-18350406 t18350406-884-punishment-3"></join>DEATH</rs>
                  </hi>. Aged 20.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">Before Mr. Justice Gaselee</hi>.</p>
